text: Schenectady County High Point is an unnamed mountain in Schenectady County, New York, USA. It is located northeast of Esperance. Oak Hill is located southwest of Schenectady County High Point. It is the highest point in Schenectady County and it is ranked 49 of 62 on the list of New York County High Points. ==References== Category:Mountains of Schenectady County, New York Category:Mountains of New York (state)
title: Schenectady County High Point
